Searching.description:
I am hugely proud to announce that my new album ‘Tesla’ is out today. I honestly couldn't have put this together without all of the support that I've had over the past seven years from you guys. You kept me going and kept me writing and I feel blessed to have such a dedicated bunch of fans. I hope you enjoy listening to it as much as I have writing it.
